HC4T3 – Defining a gradeComment Function

Main.hs
gradeComment x
  | x >= 90 && x <= 100 = "Excellent!"
  | x >= 70 && x <= 89  = "Good job!"
  | x >= 50 && x <= 69  = "You passed."
  | x >= 0  && x <= 49  = "Better luck next time."
  | otherwise            = "Invalid grade"
main = do
    print (gradeComment 95)
    print (gradeComment 75)
    print (gradeComment 60)
    print (gradeComment 30)
    print (gradeComment 110)

HC4T4 – Rewriting specialBirthday using Pattern Matching

Main.hs
specialBirthday 18 = "Congratulations on turning 18!"
specialBirthday 21 = "Happy 21st Birthday!"
specialBirthday _  = "Happy Birthday!"
main = do
    print (specialBirthday 18)
    print (specialBirthday 21)
    print (specialBirthday 30)

HC4T5 – Adding a Catch-All Pattern with a Custom Message

Main.hs
specialBirthday 18 = "Congratulations on turning 18!"
specialBirthday 21 = "Happy 21st Birthday!"
specialBirthday age = "Happy Birthday! You are " ++ show age ++ " years old."
main = do
    print (specialBirthday 18)
    print (specialBirthday 21)
    print (specialBirthday 30)

